Interface ResourceLocation<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PrivateResource, PublicResource, ResolvedResource, VersionedResourceLocation<T,V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbsoluteLocation, AbsoluteLocationWithCapability, BasePrivateResource, BasePublicResource, BaseResolvedResource, VersionedPrivateResource

    public interface ResourceLocation<T>
    Interface for resource path, both physical and logical that may contain extra information like file metadata.

      • resolveFrom

        T resolveFrom(ResourceLocation absolute)
        Rebases/resolves relative uri - called when resolving relative path against absolute.
        Parameters:
        absolute - uri to resolve against
        Returns:
        path of resource relative to the absolute uri When calling "/path/to/files/".resolveFrom("s3://bucket/") result will be s3://bucket/path/to/files/
